  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Apex Ascent</strong> is a thrilling vertical platformer that challenges your reflexes, timing, and precision. Climb towering walls filled with deadly hazards as you race toward the summit. But be warned—every step upward brings new dangers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1e6d862f95d86976668b470b4ae06bad.poster.avif?t=1763122817\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1e6d862f95d86976668b470b4ae06bad.webm?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1e6d862f95d86976668b470b4ae06bad.mp4?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate a series of intense obstacle courses where the walls themselves are out to get you. Dodge powerful boxing gloves that launch without warning, leap over rotating arms, and carefully maneuver through laser traps that punish hesitation. Every level introduces new challenges designed to push your skills to the limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1b3861348c6d5270254868324f0906c5.poster.avif?t=1763122817\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1b3861348c6d5270254868324f0906c5.webm?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1b3861348c6d5270254868324f0906c5.mp4?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're climbing for speed or survival, <strong>Apex Ascent</strong> offers a heart-pounding platforming experience with tight controls, fast resets, and no room for error. One misstep can send you plummeting—but perseverance leads to glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/658957cd4e082d807e629c1b98744a9b.poster.avif?t=1763122817\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/658957cd4e082d807e629c1b98744a9b.webm?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/658957cd4e082d807e629c1b98744a9b.mp4?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic, physics-based climbing and jumping mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unpredictable wall-mounted boxing gloves, spinning traps, and laser hazards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increasingly difficult levels that test agility and reflexes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instant respawn for rapid retries and non-stop action</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stylized visuals with clean environments that emphasize gameplay clarity</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Apex Ascent</strong> is a thrilling vertical platformer that challenges your reflexes, timing, and precision. Climb towering walls filled with deadly hazards as you race toward the summit. But be warned—every step upward brings new dangers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1e6d862f95d86976668b470b4ae06bad.poster.avif?t=1763122817\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1e6d862f95d86976668b470b4ae06bad.webm?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1e6d862f95d86976668b470b4ae06bad.mp4?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate a series of intense obstacle courses where the walls themselves are out to get you. Dodge powerful boxing gloves that launch without warning, leap over rotating arms, and carefully maneuver through laser traps that punish hesitation. Every level introduces new challenges designed to push your skills to the limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1b3861348c6d5270254868324f0906c5.poster.avif?t=1763122817\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1b3861348c6d5270254868324f0906c5.webm?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/1b3861348c6d5270254868324f0906c5.mp4?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're climbing for speed or survival, <strong>Apex Ascent</strong> offers a heart-pounding platforming experience with tight controls, fast resets, and no room for error. One misstep can send you plummeting—but perseverance leads to glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/658957cd4e082d807e629c1b98744a9b.poster.avif?t=1763122817\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/658957cd4e082d807e629c1b98744a9b.webm?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720670/extras/658957cd4e082d807e629c1b98744a9b.mp4?t=1763122817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic, physics-based climbing and jumping mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unpredictable wall-mounted boxing gloves, spinning traps, and laser hazards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increasingly difficult levels that test agility and reflexes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instant respawn for rapid retries and non-stop action</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stylized visuals with clean environments that emphasize gameplay clarity</p></li></ul>",
